Portugal Can Discuss New Measures With Opposition, RTP Reports

-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 
2011-03-14T14:28:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/portugal-can-discuss-new-measures-with-opposition-rtp-reports.html
The  Portuguese government 
reaffirmed that it is available to discuss the new austerity
measures it presented last week with  Portugal ’s opposition
parties, RTP said, citing comments made by Finance Minister
Fernando Teixeira dos Santos in Brussels today.  Teixeira dos Santos said he is waiting for the opposition
to make “concrete proposals,” television station RTP reported
on its website.   To contact the reporter on this story:
